# Secrets — never commit
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# Vendored cloud-run-mcp ships the PUBLIC gcloud SDK OAuth client here (not a user secret,
# same value as the gcp-oauth.mjs default) and the server needs it — keep it tracked.
!server/mcp/cloud-run-mcp/.env.gcloud-sdk-oauth
!server/mcp/**/.env.example

# Encryption key + local data store (contains credentials, sessions)
server/.data/
!server/.data/.gitkeep

# Dependencies
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# Build output
dist/
docs-site/out/
docs-site/.next/
docs-site/.source/
deploy/*/dist/
deploy/*/out/

# Logs / OS
*.log
.DS_Store
*.tsbuildinfo

# Editor / misc
.vscode/
.idea/

# Scratch / non-source
videos/
